            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d90266-Hd1e108">Rubrica 3</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d90266-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De laude matrimonii et eius acceptabilitate</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90266-d1e114"> 
               <lb ed="#V" n="63"/>¶ De laude matrimonii et accepta
      <lb ed="#V" n="64"/>bilitate. ¶ Rubrica. 3
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90266-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="65"/> <ref>IN genesi: et veliquea:</ref>
      <lb ed="#V" n="66"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90266-Qd1e127">homo patrem
        <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>et matrem et adherebit vxori sue: et
        <lb ed="#V" n="68"/>erunt duo in carne vna. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90266-d1e135">
               <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>
          <ref>¶ Thobie. c. 6.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90266-Qd1e139">Hi qui coniugium ita suscipi
        <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>unt vt deum a se sua mente excludant: et sue
        <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>libidini ita vacent: sicut equus et mulus in
        <lb ed="#V" n="72"/>quibus non est intellectus: habet potestatem
        <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>diabolus super eos.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90266-d1e152">
               <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>
          <ref>¶ Aristotelis hyconomicorum vel. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90266-Qd1e156">Communicatis
        <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>femine et masculi nam est maxime.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90266-d1e162">
               <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>
          <ref>¶ Iesus filius sirach in ecclesiast. c. 25.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90266-Qd1e166">Bea
        <lb ed="#V" n="77"/>tus qui habitat cum muliere sensata.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90266-d1e172"> 
          <ref>/ 26
        <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90266-Qd1e174">Mulieris bone beatus vir: numerus emi
        <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>bonorum illius duplex. Gra super gratiam mu
        <lb ed="#V" n="80" break="no"/>lier sancta et pudorata. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90266-d1e184">
               <lb ed="#V" n="81"/>
       <ref>¶ Catullus poeta. c. 9.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90266-Qd1e188">Est ne nouis nuptiis
        <lb ed="#V" n="82"/>odio venus atque parentum
        <lb ed="#V" n="83"/>Frustrantur falsis gaudia lachrymulis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90266-d1e196">
               <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>
         <ref>¶ Paulus apostolus: epistola i. ad corinthi
        <lb ed="#V" n="85"/>os. c. 7.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90266-Qd1e200"> Bonum est homini mulierem non
        <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>tangere: propter fornicationem autem vnul
        <lb ed="#V" n="87"/>quisque suam vxorem habeat: et vnaqueque suum
        <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>virum habeat. Dico non nuptis et viduis:
        <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>bonum est illis: sic maneant. Quod si non
        <lb ed="#V" n="90"/>continent nubant. Melius est enim nubere <!--268.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="115-r"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>quam vri. Solutus ab vxore: es noli querere
        <lb ed="#V" n="2"/>vxorem. Si autem acceperis vxorem non pecca
        <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>sti. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90266-d1e230"> 
          <ref>/ Idem epstola ad hebreos. c. 13. et fi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90266-Qd1e232">Ho
        <lb ed="#V" n="4" break="no"/>norabile est connubium in omnibus: et to
        <lb ed="#V" n="5" break="no"/>rus immaculatus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90266-d1e241">
               <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>
          <ref>¶ Seneca de remediis fortuitorum 21. et fi.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="7"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90266-Qd1e245">Uxor aduenticium bonum est: non est inter. il
        <lb ed="#V" n="8" break="no"/>la que vnicuique semel contingunt. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90266-d1e253">
               <lb ed="#V" n="9"/>
       <ref>¶ Lex auten. ti. de consulibus. §. alia vero non
        <lb ed="#V" n="10"/>decorabitur.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90266-Qd1e257">Uxores coruscantur radiis ma
        <lb ed="#V" n="11"/>ritorum. </quote>
            </p>
         </div>
